br><span class=\"line\">map(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;n&#x27;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&#x27;zM&#x27;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;&lt;cmd&gt;call VSCodeCall(&#x27;editor.foldAll&#x27;)&lt;cr&gt;&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">map(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;n&#x27;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&#x27;&lt;leader&gt;e&#x27;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;&lt;cmd&gt;call VSCodeCall(&#x27;workbench.action.quickOpenNavigateNextInFilePicker&#x27;)&lt;cr&gt;&quot;</span>,&#123;remap=<span class=\"literal\">true</span>&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>注意</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight lua\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">-- 这里很重要,防止光标到折叠为止,折叠自动展开</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">map(<span class=\"string\">&quot;n&quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;k&quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;gk&quot;</span>,&#123;remap = <span class=\"literal\">true</span>&#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">map(<span class=\"string\">&quot;n&quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;j&quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;gj&quot;</span>,&#123;remap = <span class=\"literal\">true</span>&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>这两句配置很是很重要的,如果不配置,在<code>neovim</code>模式下,光标移动到折叠为止,折叠会自动展开</p>\n","text":"vscode更好用的vim插件:Neovim...","permalink":"/post/vscode-neovim-plugin","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.8k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"万物皆可vim","slug":"万物皆可vim","count":2,"path":"api/categories/万物皆可vim.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"vim","slug":"vim","count":3,"path":"api/tags/vim.json"},{"name":"vscode","slug":"vscode","count":1,"path":"api/tags/vscode.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#